
  Huntail    Water Type Pokémon

  HUNTAIL’s presence went unnoticed 
  by people for a long time because 
  it lives at extreme depths in 
  the sea.  Huntail’s eyes 
  can see clearly even in the murky 
  dark depths of the ocean. 
	Evolution Chain
      Clamperl ► Huntail

 Stage 2 Forms:
  huntail
  gorebyss

